{"id":158,"date":"2017-10-05T07:43:09","date_gmt":"2017-10-05T07:43:09","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/kohette.com\/wpthemes\/narratium\/?page_id=143"},"modified":"2017-10-05T07:43:09","modified_gmt":"2017-10-05T07:43:09","slug":"post-co-authors","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/kohette.com\/wpthemes\/narratium\/docs\/theme-features\/post-co-authors\/","title":{"rendered":"Post Co-authors"},"content":{"rendered":"<figure id=\"attachment_215\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-215\" style=\"width: 1151px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter site-typeface-body typo-size-xsmall\"><a href=\"http:\/\/kohette.com\/wpthemes\/narratium\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Captura-de-pantalla-2017-10-09-a-las-15.35.56.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-215 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/kohette.com\/wpthemes\/narratium\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Captura-de-pantalla-2017-10-09-a-las-15.35.56.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1151\" height=\"120\" \/><\/a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-215\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">In the posts table is displayed the author followed by the co-authors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>In Narratium, in addition to indicating an author for your posts as is normally done, you can also define a series of co-authors for posts that have been created with the collaboration of different authors, this way on the page will appear these co-authors next to the name of the main author. In addition the posts will appear in the author profiles of both the main author and any of the co-authors.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/kohette.com\/wpthemes\/narratium\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Captura-de-pantalla-2017-10-09-a-las-15.36.15.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-216\" src=\"http:\/\/kohette.com\/wpthemes\/narratium\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/10\/Captura-de-pantalla-2017-10-09-a-las-15.36.15.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"874\" height=\"367\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>To indicate one or more co-authors for a post you just have to find the author you want to add as a co-author in the dropdown that appears inside the metabox titled &#8220;co-authors&#8221; on the post editing page. In this dropdown will appear all the authors that are registered in the site.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>In Narratium, in addition to indicating an author for your posts as is normally done, you can also define a series of co-authors for posts that have been created with the collaboration of different authors, this way on the page will appear these co-authors next to the name of the main author. In addition the [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":133,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/kohette.com\/wpthemes\/narratium\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/158"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/kohette.com\/wpthemes\/narratium\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/kohette.com\/wpthemes\/narratium\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kohette.com\/wpthemes\/narratium\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kohette.com\/wpthemes\/narratium\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=158"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/kohette.com\/wpthemes\/narratium\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/158\/revisions"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kohette.com\/wpthemes\/narratium\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/133"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/kohette.com\/wpthemes\/narratium\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=158"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}